<div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-cyan-50 dark:from-slate-950 dark:to-slate-900 min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
    <header class="space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
        Massive Virtualized Grid Benchmark
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-4xl">
        This preview runs a synthetic <strong>25,000 row x 10,000 column</strong> dataset with dual-axis virtualization,
        sticky leading columns, and keyboard navigation.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 space-y-1">
        <li>Use arrow keys, <code>Home</code>/<code>End</code>, and <code>PageUp</code>/<code>PageDown</code> to move between cells.</li>
        <li>Use <code>Ctrl+Home</code> / <code>Ctrl+End</code> to jump to first/last cell.</li>
        <li>Use <code>Enter</code> or <code>F2</code> on interactive cells to enter widget mode; <code>Escape</code> exits.</li>
      </ul>
    </header>

    <div class="h-[38rem] rounded-xl border border-slate-300/80 bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-900/80 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
      <%= render local_assigns.fetch(:massive_virtualized_component) %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
